        " رَجُلٍ زَوَّجَ أَمَتَهُ رَجُلاً ثُمَّ وَقَعَ عَلَيْهَا قَالَ \"يُضْرَبُ اَلْحَدَّ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5000 - Hammad narrated from Al-Halabi, who reported from Abu Abdullah (as) regarding a man who married off his slave woman to another man and then had intercourse with her.\nImam (as) said: \"He is to be subjected to the legal punishment (Hadd).\""
        ]
